    summerSchools.textContent = "Summer schools";
    summerSchoolsInfo.textContent = `Summer schools (in Britain they are called Summer School) is a program, usually lasting 2 weeks or more, during which attendees are usually offered intensive study of certain subjects in combination with extracurricular activities. As the name suggests, these courses are traditionally organized in the summer between school or university terms. In most cases, they involve boarding.`;




